graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    KubeRay -->|platform| K8sAPI[Kubernetes 1.24+<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    KubeRay -.->|cert mgmt| CertManager[cert-manager 1.0+<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KubeRay -.->|ingress| OpenshiftRoute[OpenShift Route API 4.x<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KubeRay -.->|ingress| GatewayAPI[Gateway API v1/v1beta1<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KubeRay -.->|advanced scheduling| Yunikorn[Yunikorn Scheduler<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KubeRay -.->|job queueing| Kueue[Kueue<br/>OPTIONAL]
    KubeRay -.->|webhook certs| OpenshiftSvcCA[OpenShift Service CA<br/>OPTIONAL]

    %% Monitoring Integration
    Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Monitoring] -.->|scrapes metrics| KubeRay

    %% Managed Resources
    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| RayCluster[Ray Clusters<br/>Head + Worker Pods]
    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| NetworkPolicies[Network Policies]
    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| K8sResources[Kubernetes Resources<br/>Services, Deployments, Jobs]

    %% Custom Resources Watched
    RayClusterCR[RayCluster CR] -.->|watched by| KubeRay
    RayJobCR[RayJob CR] -.->|watched by| KubeRay
    RayServiceCR[RayService CR] -.->|watched by| KubeRay

    %% No Internal ODH Dependencies
    Note[No Internal ODH/RHOAI<br/>Dependencies<br/>Operates Independently]

